    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>NEWARK ARENA OFFER</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Ronald Smothers</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Smothers, Ronald</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>New Jersey Gov Christine Whitman makes initial $75 million offer on what state is willing to contribute to construction of new arena in Newark for Nets and Devils; photo (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Governor Whitman weighed in last week with a $75 million opening offer on what the state was willing to contribute to the construction of a new arena for the Nets and the Devils in Newark (the site is shown here) and there was a decided groan among supporters of the $325 million project. YankeeNets and Newark and Essex county officials had hoped for a quick agreement on a state contribution of at least $123 million.</p>
        <p>Ronald Smothers</p>
      </block>
